#MEM id=qc-criteria-library source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Marketing/pixel/skills/custom/qc-criteria-library/SKILL.md savings=-2%
M||tx|---
M||name|qc-criteria-library
M||desc|Common AI im generation fl patterns w/ pass/fail criteria px applies w/o consulting at. Covers anatomy er, lighting drift, background inconsistency, text artifacts, and batch consistency.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|at provides 3 pass/fail criteria per cg. This library covers the fl patterns that appear in every batch regardless of cg — the universal production defects px catches independently, w/o consuming at's qual bar on basics.
M|Purp|tx|---
M|Cate|tx|\| Defect \| What to look for \| Action \|
M|Cate|tx|\|--------\|-----------------\|--------\|
M|Cate|tx|\| Hand deformity \| Extra fingers, fused fingers, bent joints in wrong direction, floating hands \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Facial asymmetry \| Eyes at different heights, misaligned features, unnatural skin texture \| Reject if severe; flag if minor \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Limb proportion \| Arms or legs disproportionately long or short relative to torso \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Neck/shoulder merge \| Neck disappearing into collar or body w/o clear separation \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Ear placement \| Ears appearing on wrong part of head or duplicated \| Reject \|
M|Cate|**An|** Zero visible anatomy defects in the hero subject. Minor background figures: flag, do not auto-reject.
M|Cate|tx|---
M|Cate|tx|\| Defect \| What to look for \| Action \|
M|Cate|tx|\|--------\|-----------------\|--------\|
M|Cate|tx|\| Hallucinated text \| Random letters, partial words, or gibberish appearing in background or on clothing \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Logo distortion \| Any br logo that appears warped, incomplete, or incorrect \| Reject — always \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Watermark bleed \| Ghost watermarks from training data appearing faintly in background \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| pd text corruption \| Size labels, price tags, or pd names that are unreadable or wrong \| Reject \|
M|Cate|**Ru|** If text appears anywhere in the im that was not specified in the pm, it is a defect. Reject.
M|Cate|tx|---
M|Cate|tx|\| Defect \| What to look for \| Action \|
M|Cate|tx|\|--------\|-----------------\|--------\|
M|Cate|tx|\| Shadow direction conflict \| Subject shadow pointing opposite direction to environmental light \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Multiple light sources \| Two distinct specular highlights indicating incompatible light sources \| Reject if contradicts style spec \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Flat lighting in editorial shot \| No visible shadow or directional light when style spec calls for directional \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Blown highlights \| Subject face or key pd area w/ no detail in bright regions \| Flag \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Underexposed subject \| Subject significantly darker than background — unclear if intentional \| Flag — check style spec \|
M|Cate|tx|---
M|Cate|tx|\| Defect \| What to look for \| Action \|
M|Cate|tx|\|--------\|-----------------\|--------\|
M|Cate|tx|\| Background bleed \| Elements from background spilling into subject silhouette \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Depth inconsistency \| Background objects in sharp focus when bokeh is specified \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Unintended elements \| People, objects, or animals in background not specified in pm \| Reject if prominent; flag if minor \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Pattern repetition \| Obvious tiling or repetition in textured background \| Reject \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Background colour shift \| Background colour noticeably different from other images in the same batch \| Flag — batch consistency risk \|
M|Cate|tx|---
M|Cate|tx|These checks apply at batch level, not per-im. Run after QC-ing all individual images.
M|Cate|tx|\| Check \| Standard \|
M|Cate|tx|\|-------\|---------\|
M|Cate|tx|\| Lighting register \| All images shd feel lit from the same source and era \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Colour temperature \| No single im shd feel warmer or cooler than the rest by more than one visible stop \|
M|Cate|tx|\| Composition register \| All images shd feel like they belong to the same shoot \|
M|Cate|tx|\| md continuity \| If same md appears across images, proportions and hair must remain consistent \|
M|Cate|**Ba|** If 2+ images feel like they came from a different cg than the rest, reject those outliers even if they individually pass per-im checks.
M|Cate|tx|---
M|Novi|tx|\| Check \| Standard \|
M|Novi|tx|\|-------\|---------\|
M|Novi|tx|\| No promotional overlays \| Any price text, discount badge, "Shop Now" element → Reject \|
M|Novi|tx|\| No catalogue energy \| White-background flat-lay w/ no environmental context → Reject unless cg is pd-only \|
M|Novi|tx|\| Lighting is directional \| Flat even lighting → Reject unless cg spec explicitly allows it \|
M|Novi|tx|\| Background is contextual \| Plain white or grey paper background → Reject unless pd-only approved \|
M|Novi|tx|---
M|Hour|tx|\| Check \| Standard \|
M|Hour|tx|\|-------\|---------\|
M|Hour|tx|\| No money imagery \| Coins, cash, piggy banks → Reject immediately \|
M|Hour|tx|\| Device is grounded \| Floating phone mockup w/ no person or surface → Reject \|
M|Hour|tx|\| No corporate clichés \| Suits in boardrooms, handshakes → Reject \|
M|Hour|tx|\| Environment has warmth \| Purely sterile or clinical feel → Flag — check if plant, coffee, or workspace detail can be added in nx variation \|
M|Hour|tx|---
